00:09:17.340 --> 00:09:19.350
Bird feeding is not for the birds.

00:09:19.350 --> 00:09:20.650
It's for us.

00:09:20.650 --> 00:09:23.050
They can do well without
our feeding.

00:09:23.050 --> 00:09:25.660
It is enjoyment for us human beings

00:09:25.660 --> 00:09:27.910
to bring them closer
to us in the backyard.

00:09:27.910 --> 00:09:32.150
It is supplemental to what they
get in the native situation,

00:09:32.150 --> 00:09:34.420
in the natural situation.

00:09:34.420 --> 00:09:37.810
There are only two exceptions:
If there is a severe drought

00:09:37.810 --> 00:09:42.140
in a dry area, or if there's
an increasingly hostile

00:09:42.140 --> 00:09:46.410
and heavy snow cover and ice where
