00:09:46.410 --> 00:09:51.220
Then you indeed may have some
impact on the local population.

00:09:51.220 --> 00:09:55.220
But by and large it's for
us more than it is for them.

00:09:55.220 --> 00:10:02.820
So our book, and indeed
