some elaborate modern art display

00:38:45.760 --> 00:38:48.350
of structure.

00:38:48.350 --> 00:38:52.420
I think it was in a lobby at RISD.

00:38:52.420 --> 00:38:57.040
There was leftover plastic tubing.

00:38:57.040 --> 00:39:01.140
Of course he was told by his
colleague who was in charge

00:39:01.140 --> 00:39:04.150
of the project, "Peter,
just go dispose of these.

00:39:04.150 --> 00:39:05.450
Get rid of them.

00:39:05.450 --> 00:39:06.750
It's extra."

00:39:06.750 --> 00:39:08.760 position:56%
