00:44:08.830 --> 00:44:10.520
Cleaning and disinfecting feeders

00:44:10.520 --> 00:44:14.710
and bird baths routinely
is a best practice.

00:44:14.710 --> 00:44:18.910 position:56%
And remember to change out your
hummingbird sugar water nectar every

00:44:18.910 --> 00:44:20.620
couple of days.

00:44:20.620 --> 00:44:23.650
Every few days will do.

00:44:23.650 --> 00:44:27.060
Bird feeding is important
today for many reasons.

