00:51:26.070 --> 00:51:28.670
by the National Cartridge.

00:51:28.670 --> 00:51:33.310
I mean, I always think
of cartridges and guns.

00:51:33.310 --> 00:51:41.030
So I wondered if indeed they
were promoting feeding the birds

00:51:41.030 --> 00:51:44.450
so they could shoot
the birds [inaudible].

00:51:44.450 --> 00:51:45.750
&gt;&gt; Paul Baicich: Yeah.

00:51:45.750 --> 00:51:47.900
Federal Cartridge Corporation
was for many,

00:51:47.900 --> 00:51:51.330
many years extremely
active in conservation,

00:51:51.330 --> 00:51:58.410
perhaps mainly due toward
their rural base, their owners,

00:51:58.410 --> 00:51:59.830
the family that owned the company

00:51:59.830 --> 00:52:01.740
and that still owns
the company I believe.

00:52:01.740 --> 00:52:04.190
I'd have to ask Carrol that.

00:52:04.190 --> 00:52:07.770
