00:52:07.770 --> 00:52:10.990
mainly that game birds
be they grouse, or quail,

00:52:10.990 --> 00:52:14.660
or pheasant would survive
through the winter if you fed.

00:52:14.660 --> 00:52:17.250
They had a whole series
of these PSA's,

00:52:17.250 --> 00:52:20.240
public service announcements,
as ads.

00:52:20.240 --> 00:52:24.130
They even had them, wisely enough
and this was very admirable,

00:52:24.130 --> 00:52:28.430
they had them not to shoot the
hawks that visit your chicken yard

00:52:28.430 --> 00:52:30.390
which was quite remarkable.

00:52:30.390 --> 00:52:37.330
Indeed the arms and ammo
companies in 1911 were instrumental

00:52:37.330 --> 00:52:42.730 position:56%
in forming the Wildlife Management
Institute which was deeply committed

00:52:42.730 --> 00:52:47.890
