available [inaudible].

00:53:43.020 --> 00:53:44.320
&gt;&gt; Margaret Barker: Yes.

00:53:44.320 --> 00:53:49.320
We have a lot of insectivorous
birds around right now of course

00:53:49.320 --> 00:53:54.440
and the best thing that people
can do is to plant for birds.

00:53:54.440 --> 00:53:59.710 position:56%
And even if you just have, you
know, some food plants, for example,

00:53:59.710 --> 00:54:02.260
when I go out of town I don't
